{"tenant_id": "foreign_trade_demo", "chunk_id": "auto_raw_94bab7fd53_005", "kb_id": "auto_raw_94bab7fd53", "title": "外贸客户常见问题汇总", "category": "faq", "status": "active", "visibility": "external", "source_file": "auto_94bab7fd53.md", "section_title": "问答5", "text": "问题：报价含运费吗？\n答：不一定。要先确认贸易条款，比如 EXW、FOB、CIF、DDP，不同条款包含的费用范围不一样。"}
