{"tenant_id": "foreign_trade_demo", "chunk_id": "auto_raw_9e9912bc11_002", "kb_id": "auto_raw_9e9912bc11", "title": "报价付款说明", "category": "policy", "status": "draft", "visibility": "external", "source_file": "auto_9e9912bc11.md", "section_title": "要点2", "text": "报价前要先确认产品规格、数量、包装方式、交货要求、贸易条款。"}
{"tenant_id": "foreign_trade_demo", "chunk_id": "auto_raw_9e9912bc11_003", "kb_id": "auto_raw_9e9912bc11", "title": "报价付款说明", "category": "policy", "status": "draft", "visibility": "external", "source_file": "auto_9e9912bc11.md", "section_title": "付款方式", "text": "常规支持 T/T。"}
{"tenant_id": "foreign_trade_demo", "chunk_id": "auto_raw_9e9912bc11_004", "kb_id": "auto_raw_9e9912bc11", "title": "报价付款说明", "category": "policy", "status": "draft", "visibility": "external", "source_file": "auto_9e9912bc11.md", "section_title": "付款节点", "text": "样品单一般先全款；大货订单通常先付定金，尾款在发货前或提单前按合同确认。"}
{"tenant_id": "foreign_trade_demo", "chunk_id": "auto_raw_9e9912bc11_005", "kb_id": "auto_raw_9e9912bc11", "title": "报价付款说明", "category": "policy", "status": "draft", "visibility": "external", "source_file": "auto_9e9912bc11.md", "section_title": "报价是否含运费", "text": "不一定。一定要先确认 EXW、FOB、CIF、DDP 这些贸易条款。"}
{"tenant_id": "foreign_trade_demo", "chunk_id": "auto_raw_9e9912bc11_006", "kb_id": "auto_raw_9e9912bc11", "title": "报价付款说明", "category": "policy", "status": "draft", "visibility": "external", "source_file": "auto_9e9912bc11.md", "section_title": "价格有效期", "text": "如果原材料价格波动明显，报价有效期要单独写清楚。"}
{"tenant_id": "foreign_trade_demo", "chunk_id": "auto_raw_b507894221_001", "kb_id": "auto_raw_b507894221", "title": "客户培训视频_转写样例", "category": "policy", "status": "active", "visibility": "external", "source_file": "auto_b507894221.md", "section_title": "今天这段培训主要讲外贸报价、付款方式和交期确认。", "text": "客服在报价前必须先确认产品规格、采购数量、包装要求和贸易条款。\n如果客户问报价是否含运费，不能直接回答包含，要先确认是 EXW、FOB、CIF 还是 DDP。\n样品单一般先全款，大货订单通常先付定金，尾款节点按合同确认。\n常规生产周期在样品确认和定金到账后开始计算，一般是十五到三十天。\n如果客户要求加急，一定先找工厂确认排产，不能在客服侧直接承诺。"}
{"tenant_id": "foreign_trade_demo", "chunk_id": "auto_raw_c49bcd43ef_001", "kb_id": "auto_raw_c49bcd43ef", "title": "内部售后处理口径", "category": "policy", "status": "active", "visibility": "internal", "source_file": "auto_c49bcd43ef.md", "section_title": "内部售后处理口径", "text": "仅内部使用，请勿直接发给客户。"}
{"tenant_id": "foreign_trade_demo", "chunk_id": "auto_raw_c49bcd43ef_002", "kb_id": "auto_raw_c49bcd43ef", "title": "内部售后处理口径", "category": "policy", "status": "active", "visibility": "internal", "source_file": "auto_c49bcd43ef.md", "section_title": "赔付申请资料", "text": "客户需要先提供问题图片、视频、箱唛、批次信息、问题数量和收货时间。"}
{"tenant_id": "foreign_trade_demo", "chunk_id": "auto_raw_c49bcd43ef_003", "kb_id": "auto_raw_c49bcd43ef", "title": "内部售后处理口径", "category": "policy", "status": "active", "visibility": "internal", "source_file": "auto_c49bcd43ef.md", "section_title": "处理原则", "text": "未核实前不能先承诺赔付金额。\n要先判断责任归属、订单金额、历史合作情况，再决定补发、折扣还是其他处理方式。"}
{"tenant_id": "foreign_trade_demo", "chunk_id": "auto_raw_c49bcd43ef_004", "kb_id": "auto_raw_c49bcd43ef", "title": "内部售后处理口径", "category": "policy", "status": "active", "visibility": "internal", "source_file": "auto_c49bcd43ef.md", "section_title": "升级条件", "text": "超出普通折扣权限的，需要走内部审批。\n涉及连续投诉、金额较大、责任不清的，优先升级主管处理。"}
